attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene -
Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene -

data.description: PRICE REDUCED! Custom home on private lot with no neighbors behind you and across street from pool/park/tennis courts. 2 story with master down and no carpet on first floor. Wood Laminate flooring and tile downstairs. Formal dining area opens to family room. Gourmet huge oversize island kitchen with granite counters, SS appliances (convection oven). Lots of cabinets and huge laundry room with Washer & Dryer. Fridge stays too. master retreat with soaking tub and separate shower area. Private back yard with big covered patio with brick no maintenance fencing.  Tile roof. Garage freshly painted. Close to shopping and easy access to HWY 59 or HWY 90. Located in City of Sugar Land, low taxes! Local police and Fire Station. Home warranty to buyer at closing for the first year.
